/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f44f-1f3ff.png" alt="👏🏿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />出去<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f44f-1f3ff.png" alt="👏🏿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />经过<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f44f-1f3ff.png" alt="👏🏿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />姓名<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f44f-1f3ff.png" alt="👏🏿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Bravo，Mills XXX。”</p><p>上个月（2月13日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/millie-bobby-brown-says-she-doesnt-have-many-friends-because-of-stranger-things-3837854">布朗承认，由于她花了时间制作热门系列陌生人的事情，她没有“很多朋友”</a> ：“我没有上学，所以当涉及到我自己的年龄和友谊的人们时，我没有最好的社交技能。我为这么多挣扎。我错过了一些事情。但是我正在努力。” </p><figure id="attachment_3834281" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3834281" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3834281" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Stranger-Things-Cast.jpg" alt="演员“陌生人事物”第5季演员" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Stranger-Things-Cast.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Stranger-Things-Cast-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Stranger-Things-Cast-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Stranger-Things-Cast-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Stranger-Things-Cast-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Stranger-Things-Cast-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3834281" class="wp-caption-text"> “陌生事物”的演员第5季演员。学分：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>除了布朗，<i>陌生人的事物</i>还主演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/david-harbour-gran-turismo-stranger-things-lily-allen-3479934">大卫·港（David Harbour）</a> ，<a href="https