full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/paul-mccartney-joe-cocker@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/paul-mccartney-joe-cocker@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/paul-mccartney-joe-cocker@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/paul-mccartney-joe-cocker@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/paul-mccartney-joe-cocker@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/paul-mccartney-joe-cocker@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼（Paul McCartney）</a>在今年晚些时候为已故的乔·科克（Joe Cocker）入学到摇滚名人堂（Rock and Roll）的著名作品，为已故的乔·科克（Joe Cocker）入选了一封信。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/one-hand-clapping-review-paul-mccartney-wings-documentary-3796228" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>一只手拍手</em>评论：Paul McCartney和Wings电影在工作中展示了一位大师</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-new-order-the-white-stripes-mariah-carey-lead-nominations-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-2025-3837368">宣布了今年摇滚名人堂的提名人</a>。今年领先提名的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joy-division">Joy Division</a> / <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/new-order">New Order</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mariah-carey">Mariah Carey</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-white-stripes">White Stripes</a>等人。还被提名的是已故的谢菲尔德歌手和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美奖</a>得主乔·科克（Joe Cocker）。</p><p>现在已经透露，两届摇滚霍尔入选者保罗·麦卡特尼（Paul McCartney）现在正在召集球迷，以投票赞成科克的入选。麦卡特尼（McCartney）根据<a href="https://variety.com/2025/music/news/paul-mccartney-joe-cocker-rock-hall-fame-induct-letter-1236326727/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》（Variety）</em></a>获得的一封信，该信已获得：“亲爱的摇滚乐，我想建议乔·科克（Joe Cocker）先生进入摇滚乐名人堂。” </p><figure id="attachment_3837285" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837285" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837285" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/PaulMcCartneyNewYorkBowery-second-show-rumours.jpg" alt="保罗·麦卡特尼（Paul McCartney）在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/PaulMcCartneyNewYorkBowery-second-show-rumours.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/PaulMcCartneyNewYorkBowery-second-show-rumours-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/PaulMcCartneyNewYorkBowery-second-show-rumours-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/PaulMcCartneyNewYorkBowery-second-show-rumours-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/PaulMcCartneyNewYorkBowery-second-show-rumours-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/PaulMcCartneyNewYorkBowery-second-show-rumours-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837285" class="wp-caption-text">保罗·麦卡特尼（Paul McCartney）现场表演。图片来源：Jo Hale/Redferns/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>麦卡继续说：“乔是一个伟人，是一位出色的歌手，他的独特风格为一些出色的表演而创作。他在我的朋友的一些帮助下演唱了我们的一首歌，这是丹尼·科德尔（Denny Cordell）制作的版本，这是非常富有想象力的。面板上的所有人都将意识到乔对摇滚史的历史所做的巨大贡献。”</p><p> “尽管他可能从未游说过在名人堂中，但我知道他会非常高兴和感激地发现自己应该在哪里成为如此杰出的公司。感谢您和一切顺利，”保罗·麦卡特尼（Paul McCartney）总结道。</p><p>现在可以为球迷投票，决赛入围者将于4月宣布。入职仪式的日期将在以后分享 -<a href="https://vote.rockhall.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里投票</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3843304" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3843304" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3843304" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/joe-cocker@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/joe-cocker@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/joe-cocker@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/joe-cocker@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/joe-cocker@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/joe-cocker@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/joe-cocker@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3843304" class="wp-caption-text">乔·科克（Joe Cocker）在1982年现场表演。荣誉：大卫·雷德芬（David Redfern）/雷德弗恩（David Redferns）</figcaption></figure><p>今年还提名的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-company">Bad Company</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-black-crowes">The Black Crowes</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-idol">Billy Idol</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cyndi-lauper">Cyndi Lauper</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/outkast">Outkast</a> ，Phish， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phish">Phish</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soundgarden">Soundgarden</a> ，Chubby Checker和Maná。</p><p>乔·科克（Joe Cocker）<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/various-artists-1220-1208823">于2014年末因肺癌去世，享年70岁</a>，他提名的摇滚乐大厅标志着他的第一次点头。</p><p>在今年晚些时候，大约一半的提名艺术家将入选该机构，并由1,200名音乐家，行业专业人士和历史学家的国际小组选出赢家。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-pens-letter-campaigning-for-joe-cockers-rock-hall-induction-he-deserves-to-be-amongst-such-illustrious-company-3843302">保罗·麦卡特尼（Paul McCartney）的邮政钢笔的信函为乔·科克（Joe Cocker）的摇滚音乐厅（Rock Hall）归纳：“他应该成为如此杰出的公司之一”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
多莉·帕顿（Dolly Parton）的丈夫卡尔·迪恩（Carl Dean）去世，享年82岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/carl-dean-dolly-partons-husband-has-died-aged-82-3843298?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=carl-dean-dolly-partons-husband-has-died-aged-82Surej Singh Tue, 04 Mar 2025 01:26:29 +0000 Music NewsNews..Country https://www.nme.com/?p=3843298 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>迪恩（Dean）很少在照片和公共场合见过，他在多莉·帕顿（Dolly Parton）工作了60多年</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/carl-dean-dolly-partons-husband-has-died-aged-82-3843298">多莉·帕顿（Dolly Parton）的丈夫卡尔·迪恩（Carl Dean）死于82岁的丈夫，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dolly-parton@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dolly-parton">多莉·帕顿（Dolly Parton）</a>的丈夫卡尔·托马斯·迪恩（Carl Thomas Dean）去世，享年82岁。</p><p>帕顿的社交媒体帐户证实，迪恩（Dean）于3月3日（3月3日）在纳什维尔（Nashville）去世。根据职位，院长将与直系亲属一起在私人典礼上休息。</p><p>帕顿在简短的声明中写道：“卡尔和我在一起度过了很多年。言语不能对我们共享60多年来的爱伸张正义。感谢您的祈祷和同情。” </p><div id="fb-root"></div><p><script async="1" defer="1" crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v22.0"></script></p><div class="fb-post" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/DollyParton/posts/pfbid0JUtAJRJb7CY5hPREvvv2AGEFcA2EFjGZsXqxPLP6pBgbGGP86WyanzKoTxjHbTvyl" data-width="696"><blockquote cite="https://graph.facebook.com/100044405350279/posts/1224899395666894/" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><p>由<a href="https://www.facebook.com/DollyParton">多莉·帕顿（Dolly Parton）</a>发表于<a href="https://graph.facebook.com/100044405350279/posts/1224899395666894/">2025年3月3日，星期一</a></p></blockquote></div><p>Parton和Dean于1964年开始约会，并在两年后与结。这对夫妇一起庆祝了60多年，其中59年已婚。尽管有很长的恋情，但迪恩在大多数情况下还是一个难以捉摸的人物，因为他很少在公共场合或与妻子一起在照片中看到他。您可以在下面看到他们的一张罕见照片。</p><p>去年年底，帕顿（Parton）与乡村明星邦妮·Xo（Bunnie Xo）进行了交谈，以换取<a href="https://www.countryliving.com/entertaining/a63238270/dolly-parton-marriage-carl-dean-podcast/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>乡村生活</em></a>，在那里她对与迪恩（Dean）的关系分享了洞察力。她说，在“大声”的地方，他“安静”：“他是一个家庭，这对我们来说很好。他正在沥青铺路……他正在癌症，我是摩ri座，那是兼容的迹象。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CWs-_f1lvi1/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-col