Tanya.</p><p> This idea was posed to Coolidge during an interview with <a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffconway/2025/02/27/jennifer-coolidge-talks-the-white-lotus-season-3-and-her-new-comedy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Forbes</i></a> , prompting the actress to reply: “I know! Look, it&#39;s not like I haven&#39;t wished or whatever, but it isn&#39;t happening. It doesn&#39;t matter – they don&#39;t need me. Mike White can tell a story better than anybody.” </p><figure id="attachment_3842595" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3842595" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3842595" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Greg-The-White-Lotus-season-3.jpg" alt="Gary aka Greg in The White Lotus season 3" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Greg-The-White-Lotus-season-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Greg-The-White-Lotus-season-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Greg-The-White-Lotus-season-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Greg-The-White-Lotus-season-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Greg-The-White-Lotus-season-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Greg-The-White-Lotus-season-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3842595" class="wp-caption-text"> Greg, or Gary, in &#39;The White Lotus&#39; season three CREDIT: HBO</figcaption></figure><p> Coolidge, who won two <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/emmys">Emmys</a> for her performance in the show, added that despite having to look on from afar, she is enjoying the new season. “In the first episode, I felt like – Oh, this is going to be really good! I just felt like everything he [White] set up – it&#39;s really eerie –you&#39;re not quite sure what people are up to yet.我的猜测？ Something&#39;s going to go horribly wrong. I think it&#39;s really going to go wrong. Mike White, he wants us to have it all, I think. I can&#39;t wait.”</p><p> She has also confided that she hopes Greg – who is now going by the name Gary in season three – <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jennifer-coolidge-says-she-hopes-greg-from-the-white-lotus-gets-brutal-payback-i-hate-greg-3842546">meets a sorry end in the upcoming episodes</a> . “我希望他明白了！ I hope they do something terrible to him,” she said.</p><p> She then went on to tell <a href="https://www.eonline.com/news/1414101/white-lotus-jennifer-coolidge-reacts-to-surprise-return-of-her-characters-husband?cmpid=social&amp;content=organic&amp;medium=link-post&amp;source=twitter-enews&amp;taid=67c1edfaeba5c40001b5b30d&amp;utm_medium_uc=twitter&amp;utm_program_uc=enews&amp;utm_source_uc=social" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>E! News</i></a> <i>: “</i> I hate Greg!” before adding: “Greg doesn&#39;t deserve anything good. I hope he gets what he deserves, which is something really brutal.”</p><p> It&#39;s not the first time Coolidge has voiced her desire for revenge, after saying in 2023 that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jennifer-coolidge-hopes-tanyas-husband-has-brutal-death-the-white-lotus-season-three-3452261">she hopes Tanya&#39;s husband dies in a “meat-grinding machine”</a> in <i>The White Lotus</i> season three.</p><p> Speaking to <a href="https://variety.com/2023/tv/news/white-lotus-jennifer-coolidge-tanya-husband-die-season-3-1235631644/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Variety</i></a> , Coolidge explained at the time that she hopes there&#39;s some “comeuppance” for Greg in the next season. “My hope for Jon is that he&#39;s not finished with Greg,” Coolidge said. “I hope there&#39;s some comeuppance for evil Greg. I think he should, I don&#39;t know, end up in a meat-grinding machine.”</p><p> Following Tanya&#39;s death on the show, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-white-lotus-star-jennifer-coolidge-could-be-getting-her-own-spin-off-3454682">creator Mike White said that there is the possibility of a prequel series focusing on the character</a> .</p><p> Season three of <i>The White Lotus</i> premiered February 16, with <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/the-white-lotus-season-3-review-3836677"><i>NME’s</i> four-star review</a> describing it as “TV&#39;s most essential destination”, remarking that “this transgressive soap opera remains unique and completely jaw-dropping”.</p><p> In January <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo">HBO</a> confirmed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-white-lotus-has-been-renewed-for-season-four-at-hbo-3831282"><i>The White Lotus</i> has been renewed for a fourth season</a> . Details surrounding season four have yet to be announced but it will welcome fans of the hit series “to a new destination”.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jennifer-coolidge-shuts-down-the-white-lotus-return-they-dont-need-me-3843272">Jennifer Coolidge shuts down &#39;The White Lotus&#39; return: “They don&#39;t need me”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
